{"thag1.10:0.1":"Theragatha 1.10 ","thag1.10:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","thag1.10:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag1.10:0.4":"Punnamasattheragatha ","thag1.10:1.1":"“Vihari apekkham idha va huram va, ","thag1.10:1.2":"Yo vedagu samito yatatto; ","thag1.10:1.3":"Sabbesu dhammesu anupalitto, ","thag1.10:1.4":"Lokassa janna udayabbayanca”ti. ","thag1.10:1.5":"Ittham sudam ayasma punnamaso thero gatham abhasitthati. ","thag1.10:1.6":"vaggo pathamo. ","thag1.10:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","thag1.10:2.1":"Subhuti kotthiko thero, ","thag1.10:2.2":"kankharevatasammato; ","thag1.10:2.3":"Mantaniputto dabbo ca, ","thag1.10:2.4":"sitavaniyo ca bhalliyo; ","thag1.10:2.5":"Viro pilindavaccho ca, ","thag1.10:2.6":"punnamaso tamonudoti. "}